== Amashuri yize ==
Nadia afite impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu bijyanye n'ububanyi n'amahanga yakuye muri kaminuza yigenga ya Kigali (ULK) kuva 2015-1018.<ref name=":0" /> yakoze amahugurwa atandukanye kubijyanye no gutara amakuru, kuyavuga no gutanga ibiganiro kuri radio na televiziyo.

== Umwuga ==
Umutoni Nadia afite uburambe mu kazi k'itangazamakuru kuko yakoreye ibinyamakuru bitandukanye kuva afite imyaka 15 aho yakoze ikiganiro cy'urubyiruko mu cyigo mpuzamahanga kitwa Search for common ground in Rwanda,  akora ibiganiro bitandukanye kuri television nyarwanda aho akora ibiganiro nka " Waramutse Rwanda" ndetse na "Zoom in"; akora kandi no kubinyamakuru byandika bikorera kuri murandasi.<ref name=":0" /> 

